{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/extras/gif-release-bb.gif?t=1738936551\" /><br><br><br><br>A fusion of card-based RPGs and Adventure games, \u201cBlack Book\u201d is a haunting tale of a young sorceress, who gave her life to serve the dark forces. Dive into the cold, yet alluring world of Slavic folktales - and uncover the secrets that hide in the darkness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/extras/ezgif-1-d54a5de64223.gif?t=1738936551\" /><br><br>A young girl named Vasilisa, destined to become a witch, decides to throw her fate away and marry her beloved - but that dream is shattered when her betrothed dies under mysterious circumstances.  <br><br>Aching for her lost love, Vasilisa seeks out the Black Book - a demonic artifact, said to be powerful enough to grant any wish to the one who uncovers all 7 of its seals. Join Vasilisa in her adventures across the rural countryside, as she solves the woes of common folk by confronting demons and performing exorcisms. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/extras/ezgif-1-d9986f927cf8.gif?t=1738936551\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover the seals of Black Book</h2>Unleash hellish spells on your enemies! Collect spell cards and new skills as you progress. <br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Historic Adventure</h2>Solve riddles and complete side-quests as you learn more about life in the Slavic countryside.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lead a Demonic Flock</h2>Send demons to do your bidding, but be careful -  idle demons will torture you if you don\u2019t find them something to do! <br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Myths and legends</h2>Explore a world based on Northern Slavic mythology. Learn from an in-game encyclopedia, created with the help of expert anthropologists  - and find all folk tales hidden within the game!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Knower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/08afc8c94e5d8e0111c92013c82dca55e53b85eb.jpg"},{"name":"Black Mage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/7f233e307d41567b2125fc72c7ee25f7ffe943f8.jpg"},{"name":"Keeper of Knowledge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/e18b99b084fec5e153c1bffd0d6d51ffdd22a496.jpg"},{"name":"Old Spirits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/1046394009488ebe8ae86dc309b0897d427d7936.jpg"},{"name":"New Spirits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/7b788f7c11286ef9b7936cdb932ff50593313f74.jpg"},{"name":"Sinner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/dc06c7265690fb1b71f4e3b0606830d92f4d4f2c.jpg"},{"name":"Susanin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/92b465a5284c5f9efcba53fac2e2bee1116e04d3.jpg"},{"name":"Revelation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/e2cb53cfa317c959ea4223b9cb7c830c048d5d85.jpg"},{"name":"Worthy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/304cc70e8207e9f0c1ee1737095900d816757e2c.jpg"},{"name":"Black Sorceress","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1138660/5fca18a1353aacf56180eebada3be41d10929278.jpg"}],"total":50},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738936551","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/page.bg.jpg?t=1738936551","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1138660/capsule_231x8